          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-purple-300 font-mono">
            STR: üí™ | DEX: üèÉ | CON: ‚ù§Ô∏è | INT: üß†
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Equipment System -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-900/50 to-orange-900/50 border border-yellow-400/30 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-yellow-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/images/shield-icon.png" alt="Shield" class="w-10 h-10" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-3 font-mono">EPIC LOOT</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
            Unlock weapons, armor, and magical items by hitting fitness milestones. 
