          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-yellow-300 font-mono">
            üó°Ô∏è SWORD +5 | üõ°Ô∏è SHIELD +3 | üëë CROWN OF GAINS
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quest System -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/50 to-teal-900/50 border border-green-400/30 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-green-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/images/questscroll-icon.png" alt="Quest Scroll" class="w-10 h-10" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-3 font-mono">DAILY QUESTS</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
            Complete daily and weekly challenges based on your fitness goals. 
            Every quest completed brings you closer to legendary status.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-green-300 font-mono">
            üìã ACTIVE: Walk 8,000 steps | Sleep 7+ hours
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Features -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-900/50 to-red-900/50 border border-pink-400/30 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-pink-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/images/social-icon.png" alt="Social" class="w-10 h-10" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-pink-400 mb-3 font-mono">GUILD SYSTEM</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
            Team up with friends, compete on leaderboards, and motivate each other 
            to reach new fitness heights together.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-pink-300 font-mono">
            üèÜ LEADERBOARD | ü§ù FRIEND CHALLENGES
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- HealthKit Integration -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/50 to-indigo-900/50 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/images/heart-icon.png" alt="Health" class="w-10 h-10" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3 font-mono">AUTO SYNC</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
            Seamlessly connects with Apple Health to track steps, workouts, sleep, 
            heart rate, and more. Your health data becomes your game data.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-mono">
            ‚ù§Ô∏è HEART RATE | üò¥ SLEEP | üèÉ WORKOUTS
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Retro Aesthetics -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/50 to-purple-900/50 border border-indigo-400/30 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-indigo-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
            <img src="/images/sword-icon.png" alt="Retro Gaming" class="w-10 h-10" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-3 font-mono">PIXEL PERFECT</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
            Beautiful retro pixel art, chiptune music, and classic RPG interfaces 
            bring nostalgic gaming vibes to modern fitness tracking.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-indigo-300 font-mono">
            üéÆ 8-BIT GRAPHICS | üéµ CHIPTUNE AUDIO
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-gray-900 to-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 font-mono">
        üèÜ READY TO LEVEL UP? üèÜ
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Join thousands of adventurers who are already transforming their fitness journey 
        into the ultimate RPG experience. Your epic adventure starts here.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-black/60 border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-4">üéÆ</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-mono">
          BETA ACCESS LAUNCHING SOON
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-6">
          Get notified the moment Fitscape beta goes live. Limited spots available for the ultimate fitness RPG experience.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="#" 
          onclick="document.querySelector('input[name=email]').focus(); return false;"
          class="
            inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 
            hover:from-green-400 hover:to-blue-400 text-white font-bold rounded-lg 
            transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:scale-105
            border-2 border-green-400 hover:border-green-300
            shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-400/25 font-mono text-lg
          "
        >
          <span>‚¨ÜÔ∏è SCROLL UP TO JOIN BETA</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer with Legal Links -->
  <footer class="py-12 bg-black border-t border-white/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 justify-center mb-8">
        <a 
          href="/fitscape/privacy" 
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Privacy Policy
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/fitscape/terms" 
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Terms of Use
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/connect" 
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
        ¬© 2025 Coe Code LLC. Transform your fitness journey into an epic adventure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</MainLayout> 